<i>adverb</i>: 활활 [활활], 활발히 [활발히], 활달히 [활딸히], 호쾌히 [호쾌히], 찍 [찍], 직 [직], 시원시원 [시원시원], 생생히 [생생히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>활활 [활활]</dt><br>
<dd>1. freely; flutteringly</dd><br>
<dd>새나 곤충 등이 높이 떠서 느리게 날개를 치며 시원스럽게 나는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of a bird or an insect flying freely high in the air, fluttering its wings.</dd><br>
<dd>2. fiercely; vigorously</dd><br>
<dd>불길이 세고 시원스럽게 타오르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of a fire burning strongly, wildly.</dd><br>
<dd>3. energetically; vigorously</dd><br>
<dd>부채나 손 등을 천천히 시원스럽게 흔드는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of waving a hand or fan slowly, vigorously.</dd><br>
<dd>4. freely</dd><br>
<dd>옷 등을 시원스럽게 벗어 버리거나 벗기는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of taking off one's own or another person's clothing freely.</dd><br>
<dd>5. burningly; fiercely; intensely</dd><br>
<dd>열기가 세게 오르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the state of heat becoming intense.</dd><br>
<dd>6. energetically; vigorously</dd><br>
<dd>시원스럽게 씻는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of washing oneself cleanly, vigorously.</dd><br>
<dt>활발히 [활발히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. vigorously; energetically; actively</dd><br>
<dd>생기가 있고 힘차게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being full of life and energy.</dd><br>
<dd>2. actively; busily; energetically; vigorously</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이 많이 이루어지거나 벌어지게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of doing a certain task vigorously or making a certain event occur frequently.</dd><br>
<dt>활달히 [활딸히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. broad-mindedly; great-heartedly</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 넓고 크게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being broad-minded and big-hearted.</dd><br>
<dd>2. vigorously; energetically; spiritedly</dd><br>
<dd>활발하고 명랑하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being lively and cheerful.</dd><br>
<dt>호쾌히 [호쾌히]</dt><br>
<dd>energetically; cheerfully; spiritedly</dd><br>
<dd>씩씩하고 시원시원하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of being lively and vigorous.</dd><br>
<dt>찍 [찍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. swiftly; energetically</dd><br>
<dd>줄이나 선을 세게 한 번 긋는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word used to describe one quick stroke of a pen or brush, or such a motion.</dd><br>
<dd>2. vigorously; violently</dd><br>
<dd>종이나 천 등을 세게 찢는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word used to describe the sound made when one tears a piece of paper, cloth, etc., violently, or such a motion.</dd><br>
<dt>직 [직]</dt><br>
<dd>1. swiftly; energetically</dd><br>
<dd>줄이나 선을 세게 한 번 긋는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word used to describe the sound made when one draws a line or boundary quickly once, or such a motion.</dd><br>
<dd>2. vigorously</dd><br>
<dd>종이나 천 등을 세게 찢는 소리. 또는 그 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word used to describe the sound made when one tears a piece of paper, cloth, etc., violently, or such a motion.</dd><br>
<dt>시원시원 [시원시원]</dt><br>
<dd>1. vigorously</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동이 기분이 좋을 정도로 막힘이 없는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner that one's speech and actions are pleasantly fluent.</dd><br>
<dd>2. energetically</dd><br>
<dd>성격이 좋고 활발한 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner that one's personality is nice and bright.</dd><br>
<dd>3. relievedly</dd><br>
<dd>답답했던 마음이 풀려서 가뿐하고 후련한 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner that one's oppressed mind is relieved and light.</dd><br>
<dt>생생히 [생생히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. freshly</dd><br>
<dd>시들거나 상하지 않고 생기가 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being healthy, not wilted or rotten.</dd><br>
<dd>2. energetically; vigorously</dd><br>
<dd>힘이나 기운 등이 한창 좋게.</dd><br>
<dd>With a strong power or energy.</dd><br>
<dd>3. vividly</dd><br>
<dd>빛깔 등이 맑고 산뜻하게.</dd><br>
<dd>With a clear and bright color, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>4. vividly</dd><br>
<dd>기억이나 생각이 눈앞에 보는 것처럼 분명하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which one's memory or thought is so clear that one feels like one is seeing it now.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>